      "content": "yo u ever notice how the autocomplete on search engines has been acting super weird lately?? like i was typing stuff about my neighborhood and it kept suggesting phrases that had nothing to do with what i was looking for, but they felt almost... intentional. like it was trying to nudge me toward something specific. u think that could be more than just a glitch in the algorithm?",
